Zero-waste lifestyle expert Bea JohnsonJohnson and her family generate a quart-size jar of waste per year. With her passion and positive outlook, Johnson &#x2013; &#x201c;the priestess of waste-free living&#x201d; &#x2013; launched a global movement, Zero Waste Home, and has become one of the leading spokespeople for the zero waste lifestyle. Johnson is touring South Africa during May and the Two Oceans Aquarium will be hosting her for a learning and networking event. Event details Date: 5 May 2017 Time: 6.15pm until 9.30pm Venue: Two Oceans Aquarium Tickets: R120 from Quicket For further information, go to www.aquarium.co.za.